            Mobile homes offer a lower barrier to entry compared to traditional real estate, making it easier to start building your portfolio.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center text-white/80">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Lower purchase prices
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center text-white/80">
