              </svg>
              Faster ROI
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strong Cash Flow</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">
            Mobile homes in established parks often generate excellent monthly cash flow relative to the initial investment.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center text-white/80">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              High cap rates
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center text-white/80">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Consistent rental demand
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center text-white/80">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Affordable housing need
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials Section (Placeholder) -->
  <section id="testimonials" class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
